#### text ####
text: It turns out that all the museums are closed on Mondays, so on our first day we went to Mount Takao! It's a lovely park about 90 mins west of our hotel by train that is full of interesting ecology and shrines. Because Tokyo is enormous, it's still considered part of the Tokyo metropolis, though definitely not part of the core Tokyo city.
