#### text ####
text: The start of my quest for taiyaki in Japan: Tengu-yaki! Normally taiyaki is a fish (tai) shaped pastry with a variety of sweet fillings, but this one was shaped like a tengu. Tengu are dangerous and protective spirits of mountains and forests who are associated with Mount Takao. It was delicious!
