#### text ####
text: Partway up is a choice between the Men's Stair and the Woman's Stair. The Men's Stair is 108 steps, one for each Buddhist defilement you can get purified from by walking up it. The Woman's Stair is a winding gentle slope. Despite my protestations, I was talked into climbing the Men's stair! The first of many purifications on the mountain.
